T* (Abstract) Tj
T* (Feature stores promise to bridge experimentation and serving, but the literature is) Tj
T* (fragmented across vendors and open-source projects.) Tj
T* (We systematically review 64 primary sources, propose a capability taxonomy, and highlight) Tj
T* (open gaps in lineage and point-in-time correctness.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Keywords: feature store, MLOps, systematic review, data management) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (1. Introduction) Tj
T* (This manuscript is part of a realistic but synthetic Open Journal Systems instance used for) Tj
T* (non-production testing. The content is fictional; any resemblance to real studies is) Tj
T* (coincidental.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (2. Methods) Tj
T* (The study design, materials, and analysis described here are illustrative placeholders that) Tj
T* (mirror the structure of a genuine research article so that downstream tooling sees plausible) Tj
